reviewText: I have lived in the Houston area since 1977, and it was great to see the 1950's location shots (Hermann Park and Allen Parkway).  A rare Hollywood time capsule of the Bayou City.
Another classic on dvd not to be missed , great price fast delivety safe packing...olga
